%div{id: @title}
  %section.clearfix{role: "main"}
    %article.intro.clearfix
      .item.mobilenoshow
        = image_tag('portrait.jpeg', alt:'katrina portrait')
      .item.text-box
        %h1
          %span
            %i When in Pain
          %br
          Trust Married To Massage
        %p We are committed to your health and well-being. We use the most vetted techniques to loosen sore muscles, sooth pinched nerves, calm inflamed joints and bring you back to your peak.
        %h2= link_to "Signature Services:", services_path
        %p
          Vow to Relax with hot stones, aromatherapy utilizing therapeutic-grade essential oils, deep tissue and sports massage in the heart of Midtown Sacramento, CA, with  convenient,
          = link_to "Online Scheduling.", "https://www.massagebook.com/IndependentMassageAlliance?src=external#booknow651016"
          %ul
            %li= link_to "Diamond-Grade Deep Tissue & Sports Massage & Bodywork", deeptissue_path
            %li= link_to "Cherished Chair Massage", chair_massage_path

      .item.text-box
        %h2 Pain Management:
        %ul
          %li= link_to "TMJ Massage", tmj_path
          %li= link_to "Sciatica Massage", sciatica_path
          %li= link_to "Massage for Frozen Shoulder Syndrome", frozen_shoulder_path
          %li= link_to "Massage for Plantar Fasciitis", plantar_fasciitis_path
          %li Fibromyalgia
          %li Carpal Tunnel
          %li=link_to "Golfer's Elbow & Tennis Elbow", elbow_path
          %li
            And other
            = link_to "Benefits of Massage", benefits_path
            such as alleviating headaches and stress relief.

    %article.home-text.clearfix
      %h2 Put Your Faith in Married to Massage
      %p
        We are here to offer you pain relief, increased range of motion and relaxation with the customer service you deserve!
        Your journey to full health begins with our
        =link_to "Signature Services", services_path
        which can be conveniently scheduled through our
        =link_to "Online Scheduler.", "https://www.massagebook.com/IndependentMassageAlliance?src=external#booknow651016"
        You will receive a full 60-minute massage for your hour of time when you reserve with KATRINA.
        We are located at a convenient Midtown Sacramento, CA Location: the corner of
        =link_to "21st & I streets", venue_path
        &#151; where FREE 2-hour street parking is available on I Street.

      = render 'layouts/addto'

